title: Ho's Kina
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Chinese restaurant known for its authentic Chinese tastes. Vegans will be able to find food here, such as deep-fried tofu in black bean sauce, stir-fried vegetables with tofu, stir-fried vegan lamb or chicken. The portions are generous, and the food is influenced by the Hong Kong, Sichuan, Shanghai and Cantonese cuisines. Cozy interior with a traditional Swedish pub interior.
